snippet.title: SCRAP RUSH!! - Announcement Trailer-
snippet.description: The maze-based arcade game SCRAP RUSH!! will release for Steam and Nintendo Switch in Europe and North America!  After trending in the Japanese eShop last month, the colourful multiplayer mayhem for up to four players is set to challenge friendships in the west this summer.
